prompt:
Tell me a joke about an astronaut going into space.
I remember hearing this funny joke about an astronaut who was about to embark on his first ever space mission: "What did the astronaut take with him before leaving for his space mission? His sandwich! But why would he take that, you ask? Well, you know how they say 'space is the final frontier,' and this astronaut wanted to make sure he had something from back home in his sandwich to remind him of Earth!"
